public abstract class SOM_MapRunner extends base_Utils_Objects.threading.runners.myThreadRunner
Struct to manage a runner specifically for SOM data This will launch a number of callables suitable for machine arch to manage multi-threaded calcs. Instances of this class will manage instancing and invoking all threads to execute functionality in either MT or ST environment.
